ia, F., Estimation of vapor pressures, solubilities and Henry's law constants of selected persistent organic pollutants as functions of temperature (1999) Chemosphere, 39, pp. 811-832; Van Droodge, B., Grimalt, J., Camarero, L., Catalan, J., Stuchlik, E., Torres Garcia, C.J., Atmospheric semivolatile organochlorine compounds in European high-mountain areas (central Pyrenees and high Tatras) (2004) Environ. Sci. Technol., 38, pp. 3525-3532; Wania, F., Mackay, D., Tracking the distribution of persistent organic pollutants (1996) Environ. Sci. Technol., 37, pp. 1352-1359; Webster, E., Mackay, D., Wania, F., Evaluating environmental persistence (1998) Environ. Toxicol. Chem., 17, pp. 1344-1351","Dalla Valle, M.; Consorzio Venezia Ricerche, VEGA, Via della Libertà 5/12, 30175 Marghera - VE, Italy; email: dallavalle.cvr@vegapark.ve.it",,,,,,,,00456535,,CMSHA,17258268,"English","Chemosphere",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-33846857992
